summary: We’re in an aquatic section of the Johtodex still, and today’s featured pokemon are the Goldeen line! These lovely painterly...
caption:
We’re in an aquatic section of the Johtodex still, and today’s featured pokemon are the Goldeen line!

These lovely painterly fish lend themselves specially well to watercolor so it was really fun coloring these two.  While I’ve never used one on a team personally, I always admire their beauty and power when facing them in the wild or on another trainer’s team.  Those horns and Waterfalls pack a punch!

title: Chinese Pokemon Names

summary: While green is a good look for some shinies, Beedrill was not one of them. I sort of swapped the eye color and the body color,...
caption: While green is a good look for some shinies, Beedrill was not one of them. I sort of swapped the eye color and the body color, giving it a much calmer look. I simply shifted the Kakuna coloring to a slightly more green color. And for Weedle, I gave it a nice teal coloring
